---
// src/components/Solutions.astro
---

<section id="solutions" class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-normal font-[Industry] text-pale-turquoise mb-14">
      > The Ancillabs Automation Engine_
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-6 text-lg">
      Ancillabs delivers clear, effective technical solutions that translate
      directly into startup momentum. We handle the complexity from core
      development to AI integration and workflow automation.
    </p>

    <div class="py-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div
        class="max-w-sm p-6 border rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col"
      >
        <div>
          <a href="#contact">
            <!-- <h3
              class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight font-[Industry]"
            >
              Powerful, Flexible Automation
            </h3> -->

            <p class="mb-3 font-medium">Powerful, Flexible Automation</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 font-light">
            <p class="font-normal">
              n8n is a leading-edge, fair-code workflow automation tool. It
              allows us to connect hundreds of your favorite applications (SaaS
              tools, databases, APIs) and build sophisticated, custom automation
              logic without the need for extensive custom coding. Its
              flexibility, including self-hosting options, provides powerful and
              cost-effective solutions for startups.
            </p>
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="max-w-sm p-6 border rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between"
      >
        <div>
          <a href="#contact">
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight font-[Industry]"
            >
              Tier 1
            </h3>

            <p class="mb-3 font-medium">Launch Your Core Product in Weeks.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 font-light">
            Go from concept to a live, scalable MVP swiftly. Our process focuses
            on essential features, automated cloud infrastructure, and getting
            you to market to learn from users faster.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-3 font-normal">Get to Market Quickly & Reliably</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-end self-end">
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-normal text-center rounded-sm h-[36px] gap-2 font-[Industry]"
          >
            <p>[</p>
            <p>Build Your Lean MVP</p>
            <svg
              class="rtl:rotate-180 w-3 h-3"
              aria-hidden="true"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 14 10"
            >
              <path
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="square"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
            </svg>
            <p>]</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="max-w-sm p-6 border rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between"
      >
        <div>
          <a href="#contact">
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight font-[Industry]"
            >
              Tier 2
            </h3>

            <p class="mb-3 font-medium">
              Build for Growth, Integrate Intelligence.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 font-light">
            Ready to scale? We enhance your MVP with robust features, key
            integrations, practical AI applications, and 1-2 foundational n8n
            workflow automations to streamline early operations.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-3 font-normal">Scale Smart & Unlock AI Potential</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-end self-end">
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-normal text-center rounded-sm h-[36px] gap-2 font-[Industry]"
          >
            <p>[</p>
            <p>Get an Enhanced MVP</p>
            <svg
              class="rtl:rotate-180 w-3 h-3"
              aria-hidden="true"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 14 10"
            >
              <path
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="square"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
            </svg>
            <p>]</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
